OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan pleads guilty to       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmurdering wife in car fire 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An 80-year-old man has pleaded guilty  
OL,6, to murdering his 77-year-old wife in a 
OL,7, car fire.                              
OL,9,FHelen Clarke died two days after       
OL,10,Femergency services were called to the  
OL,11,Fblaze on Sketty Lane, Swansea, on      
OL,12,FFriday 24 September.                   
OL,14,FHer husband David Clarke appeared at   
OL,15,FSwansea Crown Court via video link and 
OL,16,Fspoke only to confirm his name and     
OL,17,Fenter his plea.                        
OL,19,FHe will be sentenced on 9 February.    
